ORDER
PER CURIAM:
AND NOW, this 21st day of March, 2001, the above case is remanded to the Court of Common Pleas of Allegheny County for a determination of waiver of appellate rights.
Justice NIGRO and Justice NEWMAN did not participate in this matter.

Michael Wayne Streily, James Robert Gilmore, Pittsburgh, Robert A. Graci, Harrisburg, for the Com., appellee.
